{"name":"Greskar the Big Black Wolf","type":"npc","flags":{"btActorType":"creature","btNpcSubtype":"main","btCustomOL":"5"},"img":"icons/svg/pawprint.svg","system":{"npcType":"creature","attributes":{"soma":{"max":0,"current":0},"wounds":{"max":4,"current":0,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}},"xp":0},"background":"","descriptors":["I am a huge, mighty werewolf. I have to constantly prove my strength to stay the alpha of the pack."],"agenda":"Protect Iskra and devour as many humans as possible.","gifts":["Big Wolf: Greskar is an enormous black wolf, as big as a horse. When he grabs someone with his jaws, in addition to inflicting a Wound, he can drag or hurl them away as if they were a rag doll. Once per Scene, Greskar’s bite can inflict 1 additional Wound.","The Wolf’s Smell: Greskar’s sense of smell is infallible. The big wolf will always be able to identify someone if he knows their scent, ignoring all kinds of disguises and even magic."],"darkEgo":{"trigger":"","gift":""},"weapons":[],"objects":[],"conditions":[],"notes":""},"_id":"f48353eb49f3dfd8"}
